The workout falls under Cardio/Mat and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Comfort Moves vibe.

Original workout description: Strengthen your core and eliminate lower back pain in just 10 minutes a day! This simple, effective core workout routine will strengthen key muscles in your core to stabilize your back and decrease pain. Increase core strength in your abs, obliques, back, and hips to eliminate pain and feel better fast!

WHY DOES YOUR LOWER BACK HURT?
One of the main causes of lower back pain is weakness in your core.

Your lumbar vertebrae (your lower back bones) should be a very stable column when it is supported correctly by your core muscles.

When these muscles are weak the column becomes lax and unstable which often results in lower back pain.
